Information
------------------------------

Secret Britain: Series 3
Exploring the hidden corners of the UK in search of the best the countryside has to offer. We live in a country with some of the most diverse and beautiful landscapes in the world. It is easy to think of Britain as a crowded place, but with more than sixty million acres to explore there is still plenty of the UK for us to discover and enjoy.



3)  Devon 
On a journey from an abandoned island on the south coast to the counties most hidden and remote surf spots in the north, Ellie Harrison follows in Drake's footsteps, seeking out Devon's best-kept secrets. Chris Hollins relives an ancient and long-forgotten purification ritual on Dartmoor, and Denise Lewis uncovers the secret history of the county's most reluctant visitors.
